latestIgtvVideos.title: "I used to wonder"🌻
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
I used to wonder
if the cloud missed the rain
once she let him go.
.
I used to wonder
if the cloud called out his name
after watching him pour.
.
I used to wonder 
if they could ever forget
the words of adore.
.
I used to wonder
but I don't,
I don't anymore.
.
Cause now I see
I see the cloud shining bright
bright against the sun.
.
Accepting all of herself
and accepting that sometimes
letting go is better than holding on.
.
I used to wonder 
but I don't,
I don't anymore.
- Onella Rodrigues🌻💗
